description: Disassociates a member from a queue.

parameters.name: farmId
parameters.description: The farm ID for the queue to disassociate from a member.

parameters.name: queueId
parameters.description: The queue ID of the queue in which you're disassociating from a member.

parameters.name: principalId
parameters.description: A member's principal ID to disassociate from a queue.
